  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t截图文章地址链接：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvY29tbW9ucy9lL2VkL1NTSUQtMTI1MjU0NjdfJUU1JTg1JUE4JUU1JTlDJThCJUU2JThBJTgwJUU4JUExJTkzJUU2JTg4JTkwJUU2JTlFJTlDJUU0JUJBJUE0JUU2JTk4JTkzJUU2JTlDJTgzXyVFNiU4QSU4MCVFOCVBMSU5MyVFOCVCMyU4NyVFNiU5NiU5OSVFNSU4QyVBRiVFNyVCNyVBOF8zLnBkZg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ed/SSID-12525467_%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%9C%83_%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%8C%AF%E7%B7%A8_3.pdf\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ed/SSID-12525467_%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%9C%83_%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%8C%AF%E7%B7%A8_3.pdf</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9mRTdxeWE1LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/fE7qya5.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fE7qya5.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fE7qya5.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n这个在美国“王安VS-100” 小型电脑机器（1980-90年代流行的多终端小型机，相当于小规模的Mainframe 机）上实现的中文系统是我在首钢电子部作软件工程师时编写的，在<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41163\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41163\"><b>我回忆录里</b></a>有介绍。1986年左右得到北京市什么新技术奖状，这个截图里作为首钢的产品出售，估计是1986年之后。得北京市那个新技术二等奖时是我太太代表首钢电子部去领的奖，那时我已经在加拿大大学读研究生了。<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41163\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41163\"><b>我回忆录</b></a>里提到过这事情：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9jdTI4dUFLLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/cu28uAK.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/cu28uAK.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cu28uAK.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8yTzNibnpyLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/2O3bnzr.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2O3bnzr.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2O3bnzr.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
